title: Mommy-To-Be Lisa Haydon Poses With Her Husband In This Sweet Photo
text:
Rashmi Daryanani Feb . 20 . 2017 
Lisa Haydon and Dino Lalvani got married in a stunning ceremony last year. And this year, they’re all set to welcome their first child – Lisa has been posting some of the most gorgeous beach photos , and even made the pregnancy announcement with a bikini photo . 
She and Dino were recently at a party, and posed for an adorable picture: ❤️ A post shared by Lisa Haydon (@lisahaydon) on Feb 18, 2017 at 8:59am PST 
What fantastic vatavaran . :)
